### ── IDENTITY SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. Successful login — Admin (should return mfaPending: true)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin.mueller@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 2. Successful login — Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.bauer@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 3. Wrong password — attempt 1 (failedLoginCount increments)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 4. Wrong password — attempt 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 5. Wrong password — attempt 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 6. Wrong password — attempt 4
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 7. Wrong password — attempt 5 → account should be locked
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 8. Correct password on locked account → should still be rejected (LOCKED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 9. View profile — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/getProfile()
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 10. Update profile — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/updateProfile
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Bauer",
  "phoneNumber": "+49 69 99999999"
}

### 11. Change password — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/changePassword
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "Test@1234",
  "newPassword": "Test@1234"
}

### 12. List users — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/listUsers()
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 13. List users — Customer (should be rejected — Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/listUsers()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
